      <p>Download the petition forms here: <%= link_to "http://www.democ.org.uk/sign-petition", "http://www.democ.org.uk/sign-petition" %></p>
      <p>We are all sick of being ignored by the council and watching them ram through planning applications against residents wishes virtually every week. This is now the only way to stop the council doing this. Please join me in supporting the Residents Association’s campaign. This is really important because otherwise the Council will just keep on ignoring us all.</p>
