      <p>Many of us suffer with the problem of nuisance calls on our phones, but this can be a particular problem for people with dementia. To help with this the government is providing funding for call blockers to tackle this issue. Free call blockers will be available to anyone living with dementia who is currently suffering from scam or nuisance calls.</p>
      <p>To get a FREE call blocking device YES should be answered to the following:
